nodes.text: Docking Bay 27 was a landing bay that was located in the city Tolea Biqua on the planet Genarius. During the time of the Clone Wars, the criminals Teeku, Nawara Blen and Koobis used a modified transponder to summon the starship Starchaser IV to the bay, and the trio requested that the crew of the Starchaser transport a crate of illicit goods to the Human scoundrel Janvar Jan.
